Bokku Mart Inventory & Sales Analytics Dashboard

Tools: Power BI, SQL, Python, DAX

Designed and developed a complete retail analytics solution consisting of five interactive dashboards:
•	Executive Dashboard
•	Inventory Dashboard
•	Product Performance Dashboard
•	Supplier Performance Dashboard
•	Store Performance Dashboard

Business Analysis Performed
•	Inventory Turnover Analysis
•	ABC Classification
•	Fast, Slow & Dead Stock Analysis
•	Stock Coverage Analysis
•	Inventory Valuation
•	Reorder Alert Monitoring
•	Supplier Contribution Analysis
•	Store Performance Comparison
•	Monthly Sales Trend Analysis
•	Executive KPI Reporting

